      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It shows noticeable wear on both the exterior and interior, including visible cosmetic blemishes, surface scratches, and worn upholstery. Mechanically it is functional but may have minor issues that could benefit from attention. It is suitable for everyday use but is not in pristine shape.",
